# 2.1.0

- Fixed success/failure callback reversal if no options were specified; fixes Issue #10
  Thanks go to @benmcmaster!

# 2.0.1

- Fixed up `readme.md`
- Example app pulls from repository instead of `..`

# 2.0.0

- Support for cordova-ios 4.x and cordova-android 5.x
- Supports cdvfile://
- Can optionally resize thumbnail to desired output
- Can pull a frame from a desired timestamp (iOS only)
- Can return a base64-encoded string / ArrayBuffer instead of a file
- Can use Promises if no callbacks are supplied and the environment supports Promises
